1
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,590
<i>[Scarlet Heart 2]</i>

2
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:43,050
<i>[Episode 30]</i>

3
00:01:59,882 --> 00:02:01,632
Come in.

4
00:02:09,107 --> 00:02:13,274
Do you know what happened today?

5
00:02:13,274 --> 00:02:15,107
I've heard about it.

6
00:02:15,816 --> 00:02:20,440
When I asked you to investigate Revenge,

7
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:23,566
why didn't you realize Yin Chenggui was involved?

8
00:02:23,566 --> 00:02:25,357
Sorry.

9
00:02:25,357 --> 00:02:27,357
I'm still too inexperienced.

10
00:02:27,357 --> 00:02:29,099
I got confused.

11
00:02:33,023 --> 00:02:35,974
I'm not trying to hold you responsible.

12
00:02:38,023 --> 00:02:39,839
I'm just worried.

13
00:02:39,839 --> 00:02:45,582
If Yin Chenggui takes over Zhen Tian group,

14
00:02:47,758 --> 00:02:51,340
the company will go bankrupt pretty soon.

15
00:02:57,691 --> 00:02:59,257
Zheng'er.

16
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:03,799
We've been arguing with each other for many years.

17
00:03:04,816 --> 00:03:08,716
I hope we can be on good terms from now on.

18
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:18,382
I hope you can save Zhen Tian Group.

19
00:03:34,482 --> 00:03:36,499
I heard from your mom

20
00:03:37,215 --> 00:03:41,965
that you've put a lot of effort into Sihan's situation.

21
00:03:47,732 --> 00:03:49,266
Thank you.

22
00:04:07,116 --> 00:04:09,123
Hello? Who is it?

23
00:04:09,691 --> 00:04:10,965
It's me.

24
00:04:10,965 --> 00:04:13,940
Forget about what we talked about before.

25
00:04:13,940 --> 00:04:16,382
Here's the current situation.

26
00:04:16,982 --> 00:04:19,049
Once Kang Sihan dies,

27
00:04:19,049 --> 00:04:22,132
we'll forgive your debts to the company.

28
00:04:22,132 --> 00:04:23,340
Really?

29
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:28,466
You just need to say you already gave him the goods.

30
00:04:28,466 --> 00:04:30,132
Dead men tell no tales.

31
00:04:30,132 --> 00:04:34,340
Kang Zhentian won't ask the kidnappers for the goods.

32
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:37,674
Just remember that as long as he's alive,

33
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:41,157
Zhen Tian Group won't let you off so easily.

34
00:04:41,157 --> 00:04:42,507
Do you understand?

35
00:04:42,507 --> 00:04:45,382
You mean...

36
00:04:45,382 --> 00:04:49,674
Since neither of us want him alive,

37
00:04:49,674 --> 00:04:52,466
then we should do something.

38
00:04:52,466 --> 00:04:54,839
Don't forget he's on your turf.

39
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:56,023
Don't worry.

40
00:04:56,023 --> 00:04:58,290
As long as he's on my turf,

41
00:04:58,290 --> 00:05:02,399
I have my ways of getting ahold of the ransom.

42
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:04,090
Once the ransom is gone,

43
00:05:04,090 --> 00:05:07,257
they won't get him back.

44
00:05:07,257 --> 00:05:09,399
Okay, just remember.

45
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:12,507
You must be careful. Bye.

46
00:05:40,482 --> 00:05:42,716
<i>I said don't touch her!</i>

47
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:55,230
♫ <i>Stars are always glittering in the sky</i> ♫

48
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:57,274
<i>[Who is the murderer who killed my daughter?]</i>

49
00:05:57,274 --> 00:05:58,850
♫ <i>Waiting for the sun, only leaving after getting tired</i> ♫

50
00:05:58,850 --> 00:06:00,720
<i>[Zhang Xiao]</i>

51
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:05,315
♫ <i>Waiting for the sun, only leaving after getting tired</i> ♫

52
00:06:05,315 --> 00:06:11,507
♫ <i>I'm always in this gray area</i> ♫

53
00:06:11,507 --> 00:06:18,465
♫ <i>Waiting for you to come home when you get tired</i> ♫

54
00:06:28,107 --> 00:06:30,840
Help me book a flight to Lancheng tomorrow.

55
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:34,232
What? You're going to look for her during these times?

56
00:06:34,232 --> 00:06:36,607
Didn't we just talk about how we're running out of time?

57
00:06:36,607 --> 00:06:40,190
We have to transfer ownership before Kang Sihan gets back.

58
00:06:40,190 --> 00:06:42,882
Can't you go to her after we get this settled?

59
00:06:42,882 --> 00:06:45,907
Besides, you're still sick.

60
00:06:46,691 --> 00:06:48,482
Zhang Xiao misunderstood my intentions.

61
00:06:48,482 --> 00:06:50,049
I'm worried about her.

62
00:06:53,107 --> 00:06:55,382
As long as you know what you have to do.

63
00:06:55,382 --> 00:06:57,399
What time for the flight?

64
00:06:57,999 --> 00:06:59,591
The first one tomorrow morning.

65
00:06:59,591 --> 00:07:04,549
But Kang Siyu and Wang Tiecheng are taking the ransom to the kidnappers on the first flight tomorrow morning.

66
00:07:04,549 --> 00:07:07,282
Wouldn't it be bad for you to run into them?

67
00:07:08,899 --> 00:07:10,923
Tonight then.

68
00:07:10,923 --> 00:07:12,215
Tonight?

69
00:07:12,215 --> 00:07:15,532
The weather forecast says there's a rare storm there tonight.

70
00:07:16,524 --> 00:07:18,932
Don't you want me to get back early?

71
00:07:19,482 --> 00:07:23,199
It'll be fine as long as the plane arrives at the Lancheng Airport before the storm.

72
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:26,782
Go on.

73
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:37,923
♫ <i>No longer expecting anything from anyone, is this considered freedom?</i> ♫

74
00:07:37,923 --> 00:07:44,939
♫ <i>A promise is like dust, constantly being buried in time</i> ♫

75
00:07:44,939 --> 00:08:01,340
♫ <i>Who stills remember the confession made in heavy rain? ♫</i>

76
00:08:18,982 --> 00:08:19,839
Daughter.

77
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:21,182
Dad.

78
00:08:22,632 --> 00:08:24,649
Why are you back?

79
00:08:24,649 --> 00:08:26,532
Great.

80
00:08:28,082 --> 00:08:29,549
What's wrong?

81
00:08:29,549 --> 00:08:31,799
What's the matter?

82
00:08:31,799 --> 00:08:33,007
Nothing.

83
00:08:33,007 --> 00:08:35,607
I've just been tired from work.

84
00:08:35,607 --> 00:08:37,674
So I wanted to come home to relax.

85
00:08:37,674 --> 00:08:39,149
Okay.

86
00:08:39,149 --> 00:08:39,982
It's great that you're back.

87
00:08:39,982 --> 00:08:41,315
You're fine now.

88
00:08:41,315 --> 00:08:42,507
Come inside the house.

89
00:08:42,507 --> 00:08:43,899
I will cook food for you.

90
00:08:43,899 --> 00:08:46,382
I'll cook your favorite dumplings.

91
00:09:00,591 --> 00:09:04,899
<i>This is Xinyi's diary.</i>

92
00:09:05,758 --> 00:09:09,016
<i>She wrote down her dreams.</i>

93
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:14,149
<i>She loved life.</i>

94
00:09:15,290 --> 00:09:17,716
<i>Does she deserve to die</i>

95
00:09:17,716 --> 00:09:20,257
<i>just because she fell in love with the wrong person?</i>

96
00:09:20,257 --> 00:09:21,674
<i>You didn't kill Xinyi.</i>

97
00:09:21,674 --> 00:09:23,132
<i>My uncle did.</i>

98
00:09:23,132 --> 00:09:24,774
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

99
00:09:24,774 --> 00:09:27,232
<i>My uncle planned all of this.</i>

100
00:09:27,232 --> 00:09:30,816
<i>He put up your and Sihan's photos at the ceremony.</i>

101
00:09:30,816 --> 00:09:34,266
<i>Sorry, I lied to you.</i>

102
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:38,315
<i>After breaking up with Sihan,</i>

103
00:09:38,315 --> 00:09:40,340
<i>I had a lot to think about.</i>

104
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:42,839
<i>Sihan said I grew up with a silver spoon.</i>

105
00:09:42,839 --> 00:09:45,839
<i>I received a lot of things but never gave back.</i>

106
00:09:45,839 --> 00:09:48,266
<i>I was not considerate of others.</i>

107
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,839
<i>I must become a whole new Meng Xinyi.</i>

108
00:09:50,839 --> 00:09:53,007
<i>I want to learn to help other people.</i>

109
00:09:53,007 --> 00:09:57,839
<i>I found some information on some impoverished schools in the Northwestern mountain areas and was very touched.</i>

110
00:09:57,839 --> 00:10:01,132
<i>If I buy one less bag, I can pay for a child to go to university</i>

111
00:10:01,132 --> 00:10:03,065
<i>and change their life.</i>

112
00:10:03,065 --> 00:10:05,982
<i>That's what's meaningful.</i>

113
00:10:05,982 --> 00:10:07,524
<i>When I get back,</i>

114
00:10:07,524 --> 00:10:09,632
<i>I will volunteer to teach</i>

115
00:10:09,632 --> 00:10:12,674
<i>and let the children's laughter renew my soul.</i>

116
00:10:12,674 --> 00:10:14,139
Princess.

117
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:20,491
I will fulfill your wishes.

118
00:10:21,366 --> 00:10:23,632
Dumplings are coming.

119
00:10:25,107 --> 00:10:26,440
Daughter.

120
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:30,716
Xiaoxiao.

121
00:10:32,274 --> 00:10:33,691
Xiaoxiao.

122
00:10:36,482 --> 00:10:38,840
The dumplings are ready. Come eat.

123
00:10:42,939 --> 00:10:43,791
Smells great.

124
00:10:43,791 --> 00:10:44,732
How is it?

125
00:10:44,732 --> 00:10:47,049
Home meals are the best.

126
00:10:48,274 --> 00:10:49,491
Here, Dad.

127
00:10:49,491 --> 00:10:50,907
Okay.

128
00:10:50,907 --> 00:10:52,665
You eat.

129
00:10:58,591 --> 00:11:00,032
Delicious, right?

130
00:11:06,382 --> 00:11:07,799
Daughter.

131
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:10,399
No matter when,

132
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:12,639
I'm your closest relative.

133
00:11:13,274 --> 00:11:15,549
If you have something to say,

134
00:11:15,549 --> 00:11:17,549
you can always share it with me.

135
00:11:22,174 --> 00:11:23,632
Dad.

136
00:11:25,090 --> 00:11:29,840
There's something I don't want to keep hiding from you.

137
00:11:30,899 --> 00:11:32,349
Okay.

138
00:11:33,023 --> 00:11:36,799
If you want to tell me, I'll listen.

139
00:11:53,132 --> 00:11:54,424
Dad.

140
00:11:59,165 --> 00:12:00,999
Xinyi...

141
00:12:01,839 --> 00:12:04,340
What's up with Xinyi?

142
00:12:06,190 --> 00:12:08,982
On the day of her wedding ceremony,

143
00:12:10,023 --> 00:12:11,532
she passed away.

144
00:12:15,274 --> 00:12:17,970
Because the groom is my boyfriend.

145
00:12:18,674 --> 00:12:19,566
What?

146
00:12:19,566 --> 00:12:22,182
The groom is your boyfriend?

147
00:12:23,065 --> 00:12:25,224
Before they got married,

148
00:12:26,232 --> 00:12:28,799
I already broke up with Sihan.

149
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:32,015
Brother Kang's son.

150
00:12:35,123 --> 00:12:36,540
But dad.

151
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:42,090
I'm still responsible for Xinyi's death.

152
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:47,458
I feel so guilty.

153
00:12:48,566 --> 00:12:51,099
I can't forgive myself.

154
00:12:54,424 --> 00:12:55,965
I'm on the verge of a breakdown.

155
00:12:55,965 --> 00:12:58,307
I don't know what to do.

156
00:13:02,899 --> 00:13:05,949
I always thought I knew what love was.

157
00:13:06,982 --> 00:13:09,882
I want those around me to all be happy.

158
00:13:10,482 --> 00:13:12,523
But in the end,

159
00:13:13,374 --> 00:13:16,049
I still hurt them.

160
00:13:17,215 --> 00:13:18,639
Daughter.

161
00:13:19,965 --> 00:13:23,858
There's no right or wrong when it comes to love.

162
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:29,582
I can't give you any advice.

163
00:13:30,149 --> 00:13:32,023
But,

164
00:13:32,023 --> 00:13:35,274
the past is in the past.

165
00:13:37,149 --> 00:13:40,632
Do you still remember what I told you before?

166
00:13:40,632 --> 00:13:45,065
If you're ever faced with someone or something that makes you unhappy,

167
00:13:45,065 --> 00:13:48,140
just forget about it.

168
00:13:48,832 --> 00:13:50,599
There's still someone...

169
00:13:52,816 --> 00:13:57,965
I can't forget about.

170
00:13:59,315 --> 00:14:02,299
Do you mean Sihan?

171
00:14:06,357 --> 00:14:09,440
He's someone I thought I never had a chance with.

172
00:14:14,257 --> 00:14:15,890
Yin Zheng.

173
00:14:21,023 --> 00:14:23,316
Yin Chengyi's son.

174
00:14:27,732 --> 00:14:30,865
What's your plan?

175
00:14:34,758 --> 00:14:36,132
Come.

176
00:14:39,566 --> 00:14:41,899
Brother Zhang.

177
00:14:41,899 --> 00:14:44,049
Brother Zhang, are you home?

178
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:49,790
Brother Zhang.

179
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:52,440
- Brother Zhang, my wife is about to give birth.
- What's the matter?

180
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,691
Don't you have a car?

181
00:14:53,691 --> 00:14:55,324
Can you help take her to the hospital?

182
00:14:55,324 --> 00:14:56,882
Okay, calm down.

183
00:14:56,882 --> 00:14:58,990
Dad, remember to take an umbrella.

184
00:14:59,707 --> 00:15:00,649
Okay, let's go.

185
00:15:00,649 --> 00:15:01,524
Thank you.

186
00:15:01,524 --> 00:15:03,424
Xiaoxiao, be careful.

187
00:15:03,424 --> 00:15:05,266
- I'll get you to the car.
- Come on.

188
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:08,407
Dad, please be careful.

189
00:15:29,982 --> 00:15:31,758
Why are you here?

190
00:15:33,274 --> 00:15:35,299
I don't want to see you.

191
00:15:36,149 --> 00:15:37,432
Just go.

192
00:15:40,607 --> 00:15:42,591
What do you want me to do?

193
00:15:45,982 --> 00:15:48,507
Xinyi already passed away.

194
00:15:49,065 --> 00:15:52,407
I can't change that.

195
00:15:56,732 --> 00:15:59,732
I really didn't expect for this to happen.

196
00:16:02,716 --> 00:16:07,890
I've never regret anything I've done before.

197
00:16:10,399 --> 00:16:16,123
But I'll feel guilty about this for my whole life.

198
00:16:21,591 --> 00:16:23,782
I don't know what to do.

199
00:16:26,357 --> 00:16:28,849
There's no use in regretting it.

200
00:16:31,107 --> 00:16:33,332
What do you want me to do?

201
00:16:33,899 --> 00:16:36,149
What do you want me to do?

202
00:16:41,357 --> 00:16:43,491
What should I do?

203
00:16:45,232 --> 00:16:47,649
What should I do?

204
00:16:51,939 --> 00:16:54,574
I'm not here to ask for forgiveness.

205
00:17:00,023 --> 00:17:02,523
I just want to let you know

206
00:17:06,566 --> 00:17:08,716
I don't want to lose you.

207
00:17:29,232 --> 00:17:30,615
Boss.

208
00:17:30,615 --> 00:17:35,149
Your trip to Ganlin is a long and dangerous one.

209
00:17:35,149 --> 00:17:37,274
You must take care of yourself.

210
00:17:37,274 --> 00:17:38,749
Thank you.

211
00:17:39,357 --> 00:17:41,432
I have something to say to you too.

212
00:17:42,457 --> 00:17:45,732
Although this used to be my bar,

213
00:17:45,732 --> 00:17:48,232
it also belongs to you.

214
00:17:48,232 --> 00:17:50,440
Don't be lazy at work because I'm not here.

215
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:53,940
And don't slack off because there's a new boss.

216
00:17:54,566 --> 00:17:56,115
Don't worry.

217
00:17:56,115 --> 00:18:00,123
We'll tidy up here once you leave.

218
00:18:00,123 --> 00:18:02,032
We'll be waiting for you to come back.

219
00:18:07,065 --> 00:18:08,524
It doesn't matter.

220
00:18:08,524 --> 00:18:10,591
Making cocktails is the same anywhere.

221
00:18:11,940 --> 00:18:16,223
Who made the cocktails so bitter yesterday?

222
00:18:16,774 --> 00:18:18,315
Alright.

223
00:18:18,315 --> 00:18:19,940
We have such a huge problem on our hands.

224
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:21,940
I have no choice.

225
00:18:21,940 --> 00:18:24,315
After I find Second Brother,

226
00:18:24,315 --> 00:18:26,040
I'll go look for Zhang Xiao.

227
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:28,399
After breaking up with Zhang Xiao,

228
00:18:28,399 --> 00:18:29,816
I was jealous of Yin Zheng,

229
00:18:29,816 --> 00:18:31,982
and I was jealous of Sihan.

230
00:18:31,982 --> 00:18:36,574
But now I'm most jealous of Zhang Xiao.

231
00:18:38,774 --> 00:18:39,574
Learn from him.

232
00:18:39,574 --> 00:18:41,340
You must treat me well.

233
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:42,582
Come on.

234
00:18:42,582 --> 00:18:45,549
I'm going to get more alcohol.

235
00:18:56,274 --> 00:18:57,340
What's up?

236
00:18:57,340 --> 00:18:59,382
We made it through 2012 safely.

237
00:18:59,382 --> 00:19:01,399
What's making you upset?

238
00:19:01,399 --> 00:19:02,399
Don't worry.

239
00:19:02,399 --> 00:19:04,466
No matter what happens,

240
00:19:04,466 --> 00:19:06,482
I'll always be there with you.

241
00:19:09,274 --> 00:19:10,466
Who do you think you are?

242
00:19:10,466 --> 00:19:12,582
Me?

243
00:19:12,582 --> 00:19:15,849
I'm the famous singer here.

244
00:19:16,939 --> 00:19:18,374
By the way,

245
00:19:18,374 --> 00:19:21,958
only I like the cocktails you make.

246
00:19:26,939 --> 00:19:28,549
From now on,

247
00:19:28,549 --> 00:19:32,382
we only have each other to rely on.

248
00:19:32,382 --> 00:19:34,758
You just want free drinks, don't you?

249
00:19:35,774 --> 00:19:37,899
What did I say just now?

250
00:19:37,899 --> 00:19:39,549
You must treat me well.

251
00:19:39,549 --> 00:19:41,549
It's only been a few minutes.

252
00:19:41,549 --> 00:19:46,374
My heart is broken.

253
00:19:52,190 --> 00:19:53,799
Here, drink.

254
00:19:53,799 --> 00:19:56,424
If you don't even come to me for drinks,

255
00:19:56,424 --> 00:19:59,199
then life is truly meaningless.

256
00:20:00,299 --> 00:20:01,965
Drink up.

257
00:20:04,607 --> 00:20:09,565
Ling Dang, I'll be good to you.

258
00:20:13,482 --> 00:20:15,049
I'll also keep asking you for drinks,

259
00:20:15,049 --> 00:20:16,190
laugh at you, bully you,

260
00:20:16,190 --> 00:20:19,274
and let you feel as if nothing in this world has changed.

261
00:20:20,732 --> 00:20:24,315
Siyu, I want to sing a song for you.

262
00:20:46,716 --> 00:20:48,958
<i>Just let it be.</i>

263
00:20:49,799 --> 00:20:54,682
<i>No pain, no sorrow.</i>

264
00:24:05,399 --> 00:24:07,190
You're still alive.

265
00:24:08,507 --> 00:24:10,566
I'm not dead.

266
00:24:11,482 --> 00:24:13,315
Why did you come back?

267
00:24:15,274 --> 00:24:18,049
I hope you can save me.

268
00:24:18,049 --> 00:24:20,291
I still want to live.

269
00:24:25,215 --> 00:24:29,549
There are two guards out there.

270
00:24:30,732 --> 00:24:32,839
Aren't you worried?

271
00:24:32,839 --> 00:24:34,774
What if I hand you over to them?

272
00:24:38,232 --> 00:24:40,174
I trust you.

273
00:24:42,899 --> 00:24:47,932
You won't do it.

274
00:26:22,749 --> 00:26:25,982
Are you feeling better?

275
00:26:36,549 --> 00:26:41,199
Can you tell me about your past?

276
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:46,432
I don't want to talk about my past.

277
00:26:49,049 --> 00:26:50,840
You know.

278
00:26:52,632 --> 00:26:56,132
The first time you looked at me,

279
00:26:56,132 --> 00:26:58,457
I felt strange.

280
00:27:01,190 --> 00:27:03,765
It felt like we knew each other.

281
00:27:04,940 --> 00:27:07,257
You're still unwell.

282
00:27:08,415 --> 00:27:10,032
Get some rest.

283
00:27:10,032 --> 00:27:11,649
Do you know

284
00:27:14,065 --> 00:27:19,407
how I climbed out of the grave?

285
00:27:24,899 --> 00:27:27,591
I thought about Yin Zheng.

286
00:27:30,340 --> 00:27:32,816
I told myself.

287
00:27:34,207 --> 00:27:36,891
I must get out alive.

288
00:27:40,507 --> 00:27:42,516
Why are you quiet?

289
00:27:47,315 --> 00:27:49,466
What's your name?

290
00:27:50,899 --> 00:27:52,758
My name is Ma Yinuo.

291
00:27:56,132 --> 00:27:57,540
Ma...

292
00:27:59,215 --> 00:28:01,640
Ma Yinuo.

293
00:28:04,524 --> 00:28:06,290
I feel...

294
00:28:09,290 --> 00:28:11,632
I feel like you know me.

295
00:28:14,340 --> 00:28:16,466
Do you know...

296
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:20,282
Do you know Yin Zheng?

297
00:28:24,858 --> 00:28:26,466
No.

298
00:28:33,649 --> 00:28:36,507
I want to call my younger brother.

299
00:28:37,591 --> 00:28:39,839
Can you help me?

300
00:28:41,399 --> 00:28:46,239
The police is onto them.

301
00:28:47,566 --> 00:28:50,265
They're being very careful.

302
00:28:51,415 --> 00:28:55,340
The boss confiscated everyone's phones.

303
00:28:57,357 --> 00:28:59,840
We're in the highlands.

304
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:02,399
Without someone familiar with the area to lead us out,

305
00:29:02,399 --> 00:29:04,507
there's no way out.

306
00:29:06,499 --> 00:29:10,799
Then...

307
00:29:12,174 --> 00:29:14,591
Then we have to find a way

308
00:29:15,923 --> 00:29:20,932
to get those two kidnappers to get us out of here.

309
00:29:22,190 --> 00:29:24,491
Get us out of here.

310
00:29:27,482 --> 00:29:29,507
In your current state,

311
00:29:30,482 --> 00:29:32,199
how are you going to get out?

312
00:29:34,190 --> 00:29:36,316
You better get some rest.

313
00:29:37,315 --> 00:29:40,816
And then find the opportunity to get out of here.

314
00:29:40,816 --> 00:29:43,174
No need to worry about me.

315
00:29:43,174 --> 00:29:47,140
No.

316
00:29:47,890 --> 00:29:52,174
Ma Yinuo.

317
00:29:52,732 --> 00:29:54,620
Believe me.

318
00:29:59,549 --> 00:30:01,132
We...

319
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:05,007
We...

320
00:30:06,715 --> 00:30:15,807
We'll get out of here alive.

321
00:30:42,982 --> 00:30:44,799
What are you thinking about?

322
00:30:50,939 --> 00:30:53,215
Can you let go of your hatred?

323
00:31:03,482 --> 00:31:05,882
Can we not talk about this?

324
00:31:08,649 --> 00:31:11,040
If we want to be together,

325
00:31:11,791 --> 00:31:14,257
I hope we can stay away from hatred.

326
00:31:19,399 --> 00:31:22,132
I can't decide this on my own.

327
00:31:24,190 --> 00:31:26,266
I don't have a choice.

328
00:31:30,524 --> 00:31:33,140
What if I need you to give up?

329
00:31:35,982 --> 00:31:37,566
This is my own business.

330
00:31:37,566 --> 00:31:40,032
Why do you want to be involved?

331
00:31:41,607 --> 00:31:43,357
It has nothing to do with you.

332
00:31:43,357 --> 00:31:45,323
But you're involved.

333
00:31:47,023 --> 00:31:50,420
I don't want to see you hurt yourself

334
00:31:50,420 --> 00:31:54,520
and other people because of resentment.

335
00:31:58,315 --> 00:32:00,682
I know what I'm doing.

336
00:32:01,649 --> 00:32:04,057
I will bear all the consequences.

337
00:32:09,424 --> 00:32:11,415
Xinyi's death

338
00:32:12,649 --> 00:32:15,058
already caused us so much pain.

339
00:32:17,290 --> 00:32:19,791
Why can't you understand?

340
00:32:27,939 --> 00:32:30,816
I already made up my mind.

341
00:32:30,816 --> 00:32:33,015
Please don't intervene, okay?

342
00:32:52,065 --> 00:32:54,257
If that's the case,

343
00:32:57,274 --> 00:32:59,290
come find me

344
00:33:00,132 --> 00:33:02,132
after you figure it out.

345
00:33:06,649 --> 00:33:08,758
You can sleep here tonight.

346
00:33:11,274 --> 00:33:13,291
I'll go to my dad's room.

347
00:33:35,149 --> 00:33:37,649
Xiao Wei, give me the hospital's address.

348
00:33:37,649 --> 00:33:38,582
I'm coming now.

349
00:33:38,582 --> 00:33:40,107
I will be there soon.

350
00:34:15,732 --> 00:34:17,249
Zhang Xiao.

351
00:34:21,482 --> 00:34:22,958
Zhang Xiao.

352
00:34:31,023 --> 00:34:32,624
Zhang Xiao.

353
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:57,970
<i>Your call will go to voicemail.</i>

354
00:34:57,970 --> 00:34:59,800
<i>You will be charged after the tone.</i>

355
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,550
<i>Please hang up if you're not leaving a message.</i>

356
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:05,410
<i>Please press the button after leaving your message.</i>

357
00:35:07,691 --> 00:35:11,816
Zhang Xiao, I didn't see you after I woke up.

358
00:35:11,816 --> 00:35:13,299
Where are you?

359
00:35:16,749 --> 00:35:18,691
I'm waiting for you at home.

360
00:35:20,524 --> 00:35:21,840
Bye.

361
00:35:27,691 --> 00:35:29,074
Dad.

362
00:35:29,899 --> 00:35:31,940
Is your hand still in pain?

363
00:35:32,566 --> 00:35:34,774
It's not painful anymore after taking the medicine.

364
00:35:34,774 --> 00:35:36,190
Don't worry, it's just a small injury.

365
00:35:36,190 --> 00:35:37,357
I'll be fine after a few days.

366
00:35:37,357 --> 00:35:40,215
The pain will last a hundred days.

367
00:35:40,215 --> 00:35:43,774
I was so scared when I got Xiao Wei's call.

368
00:35:43,774 --> 00:35:48,023
Yes, I was lucky I got in the accident on the way home from the hospital.

369
00:35:48,023 --> 00:35:52,039
Otherwise, Xiao Wei's wife would've been in big trouble.

370
00:36:08,540 --> 00:36:11,070
<i>Your call will go to voicemail.</i>

371
00:36:11,070 --> 00:36:12,890
<i>You will be charged after the tone.</i>

372
00:36:12,890 --> 00:36:14,982
<i>Please hang up if you're not leaving a message.</i>

373
00:36:14,982 --> 00:36:16,490
Director Yin.

374
00:36:19,065 --> 00:36:20,274
What are you doing here?

375
00:36:20,274 --> 00:36:23,732
I don't think you would've gone back if I didn't come.

376
00:36:23,732 --> 00:36:25,566
I got the notice from the Industry and Commerce Bureau.

377
00:36:25,566 --> 00:36:27,982
The change of legal representative requires signatures.

378
00:36:27,982 --> 00:36:29,749
The accountant and lawyer is already there.

379
00:36:29,749 --> 00:36:32,274
You must go back today.

380
00:36:32,274 --> 00:36:34,357
I already booked the flight.

381
00:36:34,357 --> 00:36:36,424
We must go to the airport now.

382
00:36:37,249 --> 00:36:38,774
If you don't go back today,

383
00:36:38,774 --> 00:36:40,482
we don't know when our next chance is.

384
00:36:40,482 --> 00:36:44,282
Your efforts will all go to waste.

385
00:36:45,999 --> 00:36:47,315
Wait for me in the car.

386
00:36:47,315 --> 00:36:48,707
Okay.

387
00:36:54,691 --> 00:36:59,057
Zhang Xiao, I keep calling you, but you're not picking up.

388
00:36:59,057 --> 00:37:00,440
Something urgent came up.

389
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,249
I have to go back now.

390
00:37:02,940 --> 00:37:05,040
Don't worry.

391
00:37:05,040 --> 00:37:07,566
After I settle everything,

392
00:37:07,566 --> 00:37:10,790
I will come back for you, okay?

393
00:37:11,799 --> 00:37:13,165
Wait for me.

394
00:37:22,649 --> 00:37:24,557
Director Yin, get in the car.

395
00:37:41,549 --> 00:37:42,882
Dad.

396
00:37:44,399 --> 00:37:46,182
Thank you, Sir.

397
00:37:49,540 --> 00:37:51,007
Be careful.

398
00:37:55,882 --> 00:37:57,649
Dad.

399
00:37:57,649 --> 00:38:01,440
A friend came to visit me last night.

400
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:03,374
He spent the night at our house.

401
00:38:04,315 --> 00:38:06,649
Alright, do I know him?

402
00:38:07,257 --> 00:38:10,458
Let's go inside first.

403
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:13,949
Okay.

404
00:38:15,482 --> 00:38:17,765
I'll go in first.

405
00:38:46,474 --> 00:38:47,758
Dad.

406
00:38:48,524 --> 00:38:50,558
Can I borrow your phone?

407
