♫ <i>Stopping in place</i> ♫

409
00:39:02,899 --> 00:39:07,580
♫ <i>Not knowing how to keep going</i> ♫

410
00:39:07,580 --> 00:39:09,340
<i>[Add to Blacklist]</i>

411
00:39:09,340 --> 00:39:12,065
♫ <i>I hug you tightly</i> ♫

412
00:39:12,065 --> 00:39:15,090
♫ <i>The words of deep love</i> ♫

413
00:39:15,090 --> 00:39:17,507
♫ <i>Like the end of a movie, separated by each scene</i> ♫

414
00:39:17,507 --> 00:39:18,999
Who is it?

415
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:21,507
An unknown number.

416
00:39:23,315 --> 00:39:28,882
♫ <i>Seething endlessly</i> ♫

417
00:39:29,549 --> 00:39:35,215
♫ <i>Every night I wake up from my empty dream</i> ♫

418
00:39:35,215 --> 00:39:40,999
♫ <i>Losing you is like losing everything</i> ♫

419
00:39:40,999 --> 00:39:45,174
♫ <i>Who remembers the day we broke up?</i> ♫

420
00:39:45,174 --> 00:39:47,240
<i>This is his decision.</i>

421
00:39:49,215 --> 00:39:51,132
<i>He chose to leave.</i>

422
00:39:53,232 --> 00:39:54,907
<i>He chose to leave me.</i>

423
00:40:04,340 --> 00:40:09,332
Daughter, who is your friend?

424
00:40:12,982 --> 00:40:15,949
You said he was inside, but he's not here anymore.

425
00:40:20,899 --> 00:40:24,939
Is your friend Yin Zheng?

426
00:40:49,190 --> 00:40:53,049
Xiaoxiao, we'll be very busy the next few days.

427
00:40:53,049 --> 00:40:55,649
I forgot to tell you something.

428
00:40:55,649 --> 00:40:57,566
Because of my job,

429
00:40:57,566 --> 00:40:59,424
I already sold the house.

430
00:40:59,424 --> 00:41:01,482
I bought a house in the west.

431
00:41:01,482 --> 00:41:04,839
We're moving tomorrow.

432
00:41:04,839 --> 00:41:06,923
Tomorrow?

433
00:41:06,923 --> 00:41:08,099
Yes.

434
00:41:09,549 --> 00:41:12,166
Get your stuff packed.

435
00:41:37,023 --> 00:41:38,424
Too much Renminbi?

436
00:41:38,424 --> 00:41:40,674
You had to exchange them for American dollars?

437
00:41:41,982 --> 00:41:44,674
Let's go to the factory first.

438
00:41:44,674 --> 00:41:46,549
We're strangers to this area.

439
00:41:46,549 --> 00:41:50,691
Maybe they'll know where the kidnappers are.

440
00:41:50,691 --> 00:41:52,058
Okay.

441
00:42:07,152 --> 00:42:08,860
Are you sure it's here?

442
00:42:11,427 --> 00:42:12,678
Yes.

443
00:42:12,678 --> 00:42:14,094
Don't look down on this factory.

444
00:42:14,094 --> 00:42:15,552
They have everything we need.

445
00:42:15,552 --> 00:42:17,969
Don't judge a book by its cover.

446
00:42:21,860 --> 00:42:24,610
Director Wang, come.

447
00:42:24,610 --> 00:42:26,611
Hello, Mr. Kang.

448
00:42:26,611 --> 00:42:28,302
- Just give it to me.
- It's okay.

449
00:42:28,302 --> 00:42:30,511
- Come in and take a seat.
- Okay.

450
00:42:30,511 --> 00:42:32,411
The wind is strong today.

451
00:42:32,411 --> 00:42:34,002
Yes.

452
00:42:39,810 --> 00:42:41,050
Hello?

453
00:42:43,736 --> 00:42:46,169
Okay, don't worry. I got it.

454
00:42:49,511 --> 00:42:50,860
I can't believe it.

455
00:42:50,860 --> 00:42:53,235
After Mr. Kang left the factory,

456
00:42:53,235 --> 00:42:55,636
he was met with such misfortune.

457
00:42:56,377 --> 00:42:58,552
Is the ransom inside the box?

458
00:42:58,552 --> 00:43:00,344
It's not safe to have it on you.

459
00:43:00,344 --> 00:43:02,943
It's most safe inside our factory's safe.

460
00:43:02,943 --> 00:43:03,859
It's okay.

461
00:43:03,859 --> 00:43:05,985
I think the kidnappers will call me at any time.

462
00:43:05,985 --> 00:43:07,860
I'll keep it on me.

463
00:43:08,636 --> 00:43:10,159
Okay, sure.

464
00:43:10,159 --> 00:43:12,444
I already arranged the hotel for you.

465
00:43:12,444 --> 00:43:14,152
Let's go over there in a bit.

466
00:43:14,152 --> 00:43:15,235
It's okay.

467
00:43:15,235 --> 00:43:17,210
We already book our hotel.

468
00:43:18,527 --> 00:43:19,869
Alright.

469
00:43:19,869 --> 00:43:21,969
Then come in for some tea.

470
00:43:21,969 --> 00:43:22,985
Okay, let's go.

471
00:43:22,985 --> 00:43:24,760
Let's go.
